{"batchNumber":183,"issues":[{"number":3030,"title":"spring-ai-bedrock-converse-spring-boot-starter is missing in pring-ai-bom 1.0.0-M8","body":"The dependency \n```\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.ai</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-ai-bedrock-converse-spring-boot-starter</artifactId>\n</dependency>\n```\nis missing in \n```\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.ai</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-ai-bom</artifactId>\n  <version>1.0.0-M8</version>\n  <type>pom</type>\n  <scope>import</scope>\n</dependency>\n```","state":"CLOSED","createdAt":[2025,5,7,16,14,59],"updatedAt":[2025,5,15,7,23,43],"closedAt":[2025,5,15,7,23,43],"url":"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/issues/3030","author":{"login":"brunorabaca","name":""},"comments":[{"author":{"login":"dafriz","name":"David Frizelle"},"body":"From M6 to M7 there were artifact id changes for the model starters:\n\nspring-ai-{model}-spring-boot-starter → spring-ai-starter-model-{model}\n\nTry this instead\n\n```\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.ai</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-ai-starter-model-bedrock-converse</artifactId>\n</dependency>\n```\n","createdAt":[2025,5,8,12,8,47]},{"author":{"login":"brunorabaca","name":""},"body":"Thank you @dafriz it worked.","createdAt":[2025,5,12,15,23,41]}],"labels":[]}],"timestamp":"2025-07-24_17-14-48"}